## 6. Armour System Summary

|Mechanic                          |Rule                                                               |
|----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Physical attacks vs Armour        |Damage reduced by Armour value, minimum 100                        |
|Spells vs Armour                  |Depends on school: PHYSICAL / ARCANE reduce (min 100); VOID lineage and TRUE_DMG bypass|
|Armour Break vs Armour            |Reduces Armour first, excess converts to flat bonus physical damage. Amplifies any non-bypassing damage (incl. PHYSICAL/ARCANE spells).|
|Armour Break vs no Armour         |Functions as flat bonus physical damage only                       |
|Corruption vs Armour (Branch 3 T0)|Each corruption stack reduces target Armour by 100                 |
|Armour to ATK (Branch 1 T2)       |All friendly Humans gain ATK equal to their Armour value           |
|Armour gain doubling (Branch 1 T3)|All Armour gains on Abyssal Knight are doubled                     |

